# Nexus Core - Enterprise AI Workspace

This repository houses the dynamic PHP/MySQL MVC iteration of the Nexus Core platform, serving as an enterprise IT ticket and equipment replacement tracking system.

---

## 📂 File Structure

Below is an overview of the key components and layout of the repository:

```text
├── config/
│   └── database.php           # PDO database connection provider
├── middleware/
│   └── AuthMiddleware.php     # Class-based privilege & role-level access validation
├── api/
│   └── tasks.php              # Backend controller for tickets, quotations, and replacement CRUD
├── components/
│   ├── replacement.component.js # Replacement request CRUD, modal forms, and review tables
│   ├── drawers.component.js   # Client bar alerts & notification modals
│   ├── auth.component.js      # Session login/logout controls
│   └── charts.component.js    # Dashboard analytics and data widgets
├── app.js                     # Main client-side router & workspace view manager
├── index.php                  # Main entry point and frame structure of the app
├── replacement_report.php     # Printable/exportable PDF replacement request document template
├── readme                     # Developer documentation and project reference
└── scratch/                   # DB migrations, test scripts, and data seeders
```

---

## 🛠️ Technology Stack

The project is built using a dynamic client-server structure:
* **Backend & API**: **PHP** (PDO database queries, class-based [AuthMiddleware](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/InsBinomo/middleware/AuthMiddleware.php) validation, and JSON controllers like [tasks.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/InsBinomo/api/tasks.php)).
* **Frontend Routing & UI**: **JavaScript (ES6+)** (Dynamic view manager in [app.js](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/InsBinomo/app.js) and reusable modular UI components in [components/](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/InsBinomo/components)).
* **Styling**: **Tailwind CSS & CSS** (Tailwind configuration and custom styles from [index.css](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/InsBinomo/index.css) loaded in [index.php](file:///c:/xampp/htdocs/InsBinomo/index.php)).
* **Database**: **MySQL** (Structured relational database querying).

---

## ✨ System Features

### 🛠️ Ticket & Diagnosis Management
*   **Technician Permissions**: Technicians are restricted from closing tickets (which returns an `"Access Denied"` error) but retain full access to update fields in the **Diagnosis Status** section.
*   **Quotation Approval Actions**: When a quote is approved, administrators/coordinators are presented with status progression options:
    1.  Reassign to the first assigned technician.
    2.  Show technician selection dropdown to assign to another technician.
    3.  Move back to Pending with a visible `Quotation Approval` tag.
*   **Seeding & Truncating**: Database ticket mock-ups can be dynamically seeded via `seed_test_tasks.php` or cleared completely via `clear_all_tasks.php`.

### 📦 Equipment Replacement Requests
*   **Secondary Status Lifecycle**: Every replacement request tracks a secondary delivery/courier status (`Under Review`, `Arranged By Courier`, `Normal Delivery`, `Delivered`, `Waiting`). If status is `Waiting`, a custom sub-reason is recorded (e.g. *Waiting for Parts*).
*   **Waiting Replacements Datatable**: A dedicated "Waiting Replacement" navigation section and datatable lists all requests currently in `Waiting` secondary status, featuring dynamic search, filters (priority, device type), and row actions.
*   **Separate Status Control**: In the main Replacement Log table, authorized coordinators/managers can click a separate sliders/settings button (`Set Status`) to directly change the main status, verifier details, and secondary courier/waiting states without having to edit the full request details.
*   **passcode Verification**: The delete button under the replacement log requires typing a 6-digit administrative passcode (`992110`) before executing.
*   **Event Notifications**: Any status changes (Approved, Rejected, Cancelled) or updates (Edited) automatically dispatch real-time alerts to the assigned salesman and coordinators.
*   **PDF Generation & Clean Reports**: Supports client-side PDF export via `replacement_report.php` showing clean customer/authorised signatures in a 3-column footer alignment.

